{"tid":1019134,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［二十四孝］幫我阿爺教仔","createTime":"2019-02-12T17:37:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T18:04:38.000Z","uid":13062,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2688175108cd0ce986b92956a85fe956cdfac740","tid":1019134,"uid":13062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:37:17.000Z","msg":"唔知呢度有無巴打嘅阿爸同我老竇一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係屋企入面，乜都睇唔過眼，唔理啱唔啱乜都要鬧一餐，好似咁樣先有威嚴咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就好似喺屋企做家務咁，我掛啲毛巾，我問邊一條係佢嘅，佢都可以鬧我問我係咪盲嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬呀！啲毛巾一個月換一次，又唔係我嘅，鬼知你邊條咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由於我都幾唔服氣，於是嬲嬲地入廁所拎咗我同阿哥條洗面巾出黎問佢分唔分到。佢開頭唔答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話你估我真係唔知咩，比我逼多兩逼，<br />\n佢好撚胸有成竹咁指住左邊嗰條，結果......<br />\n<strong>梗係錯撚咗</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n於是我一口氣用佢頭先鬧我嘅說話，鬧翻佢轉頭，<br />\n依家佢嬲到坐咗係個廳到冇聲出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e652ee75dde59e7f2b258b3e888b8b50efc221","tid":1019134,"uid":13062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:40:10.000Z","msg":"個個都好似我老竇咁冇聲出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d625f0a0b7119ca0f0ea6c5e4d9da7a4862d9669","tid":1019134,"uid":221857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:43:54.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"08a3be7381192e0b3c966c2f1daacb5215d6181d","tid":1019134,"uid":13062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d625f0a0b7119ca0f0ea6c5e4d9da7a4862d9669","tid":1019134,"uid":221857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:43:54.000Z","msg":"2/10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T17:49:24.000Z","msg":"真人真事，頭先條氣仲chok住chok，而家舒服晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57